 python3,
 python3-gi,
 python3-nautilus
Description: Nautilus extension to change folder colors and icons
 KAFOLCOLOR adds a Nautilus context menu for local folders, allowing users
 to apply predefined folder colors, choose custom icons, open a GTK4 icon
 gallery, and restore the original folder icon using GNOME metadata.
